每年的；年度的；一年的；一年一次的；一年一度的；全年的；一年生的；年常的；年度发生的
年刊；年报；年鉴；一年生植物；周年纪念刊物；年度总结刊物

1.en: If you've got a great item of clothing, like a dress shirt, why not get more wear out of it than the annual outing for new year?
1.cn: 如果你有一套很棒的衣服，比如一件礼服衬衫，为什么不在新的一年中比往常穿更多次呢？

2.en: Who will be your sponsor? How much is his annual income and what will be the amount you will receive annually?
2.cn: 谁资助你？他每年的收入是多少？每年会资助你多少？

3.en: Mr Rato said he expected to be given a clear mandate to implement a two-stage reform at the fund's annual meeting next month in Singapore.
3.cn: 拉托表示，自己期望得到明确授权，以便在下个月的IMF新加坡年会上开始实施两阶段改革计划。

0.en: Hey, Stuart, I see you're getting ready for your Halloween party. Yeah, it's my annual attempt to meet women. Ninth time's the charm.
0.cn: 斯图尔特，你开始为万圣节派对做准备啦。这可是我每年的泡妞时节呢，希望第九次可以手到妞来。

1.en: MU's Greek Council. We sponsor the annual Scare Games.
1.cn: 怪大学生会，我们主办年度惊吓杯。

2.en: She won a thousand dollars. So this is an annual thing?
2.cn: 她为我们赢得了一千美元！啊，是一年一次的吗？

3.en: The what? It's an annual science conference. We've all been invited to speak.
3.cn: 什么？是一个年度科学会议，我们都被邀请发言。

4.en: 200 million Chinese leave the cities, the biggest annual migration of people on the planet.
4.cn: 两亿国民离开城市，是规模最大的年度人口迁移，冠绝全球。

5.en: The Fifth Annual East Rutherford, New Jersey, Gay, Lesbian, Bisexual and Transgender Alliance Luau.
5.cn: 第五届新泽西州东卢瑟福德男同，女同，双性恋者和变性人联盟宴会。

6.en: To cope with a 30 million annual visitors, the Chinese have built the world's highest outdoor elevator.
6.cn: 为了满足每年三千万人次的游客，中国修建了世界上最高的户外电梯。

7.en: Okay, I can breathe again. Babe, they want to have sex. Oh, of course! The annual birthday booty spectacular!
7.cn: 好了，我又能呼吸了。亲爱的，他们想做爱。当然啊，年度生日庆祝打炮大典！

8.en: But one day, before the opening night of our school's annual musical, he walked up to me and holding a letter.
8.cn: 但是有一天在我们学校年度音乐会的前一个晚上，他走到我面前，拿着一封信。

9.en: Then the annual school fundraiser arrived and I found myself with a whole new set of problems. I was a Basketboy.
9.cn: 学校一年一度的筹款活动到了，我陷入一堆新难题。我要做篮子男孩。

10.en: Chuck's dad, Bart bass, is hosting the annual brunch for his foundation. Everyone is invited. Well, not everyone.
10.cn: 恰克的爸爸，巴特·拜斯，为他的基金会举办每年一度的早午餐会，所有人都得到邀请了，不是所有人。

11.en: I remember it distinctly because I had just composed my annual poem commemorating the anniversary of Dr. Seuss's death.
11.cn: 我记得非常清楚，因为当时我刚创作了一首年度诗歌，以在苏斯博士的逝世纪念日追忆他。

12.en: Simple binary pings on an annual basis give us some clue as to which worlds have potential. And one system shows promise.
12.cn: 每年用简单的二进制方式进行分析我们得到了一些线索 哪些地方存在可能有一个很有希望的星系

13.en: Now that I'm no longer with Amy, I have an extra ticket to the annual Thanksgiving lunch buffet at the aquarium cafeteria. Who wants it?
13.cn: 鉴于我跟艾米已经分手了，我有多一张水族馆餐厅的年度感恩节自助午餐票，谁想要啊？
